Originally ripped by Terminal Escape, posted on October 01, 2024 Description from Terminal Escape:
 Threw this one on when I was digging through the 'to be listened to' box and ended up sticking with it for a couple of rounds. Some folks gonna listen to COCKSPARRER or some other kind of infectious street punk with hopelessly addictive choruses....but me? I'm gonna hum along to this shit I can't understand and crank "Menghancurkan Dan Membangun" for the third time in a row.UNTUKNU KOMUNITAS••••SUBHUMANS hit Templeton, California with HUMAN tonight.Always pysched to see them in a smaller town, but particularly and specifically excited to sneak away to Paso Robles with Kelsey and hit The Vreamery.
